
Intro
-----

My personal vim/gvim setup.

Run ``deploy.sh`` to deploy to the current user's home directory:
 
   * dotvim/ -> ~/.vim/
   * dotvimrc -> ~/.vimrc
   * dotgvimrc -> ~/.gvimrc

The ``get_modules.sh`` script sets up some vim plugins as submodules to this repo (based on the very good write-up @ http://sontek.net/turning-vim-into-a-modern-python-ide).


